stories.text:
I tried to upload a WebP image to Google Keep(Google's version of online Notes) and it said upload failed then I converted it to JPEG and it worked.

Maybe it's just me but if it is true I found it funny that they do not support compressed image format that they created.

WebP: https://developers.google.com/speed/webp

Google Keep: https://keep.google.com
stories.title: Google Keep doesn't support image format that Google created
